        "title": "refactor: migrate bundled transcript target lookups",
        "body": "## What\n\nMigrates bundled Discord and Telegram transcript target lookup paths onto the scoped transcript runtime APIs, while preserving current file-backed behavior and Telegram command `sessionFile` compatibility where that remains part of the command context.\n\n## Why\n\nThis is part of the Path 3 SQLite branch-by-abstraction stack. These bundled callers were still deriving concrete transcript files from mutable session-store state, which blocked bundled-plugin SQLite validation from exercising storage-neutral transcript target APIs.\n\nRefs #88838.\n\n## Changes\n\n- Read scoped transcript events\n- Publish Telegram transcript updates\n- Preserve command compatibility\n- Add visible-text helper\n- Update focused tests\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `extensions/discord/src/monitor/message-handler.process.ts` | Reads final assistant text from scoped transcript events |\n| `extensions/telegram/src/bot-message-dispatch.ts` | Uses scoped writer/publisher APIs for mirror writes |\n| `extensions/telegram/src/bot-native-commands.ts` | Resolves scoped target while preserving command `sessionFile` |\n| `src/plugin-sdk/text-chunking.ts` | Exposes phase-aware assistant text extraction |\n| `extensions/*/*.test.ts` | Updates Discord/Telegram regression coverage |\n\n## Testing\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/discord/src/monitor/message-handler.process.test.ts extensions/telegram/src/bot-native-commands.session-meta.test.ts extensions/telegram/src/bot-message-dispatch.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/plugin-sdk/session-transcript-runtime.test.ts src/plugin-sdk/session-transcript-hit.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/transcript-runtime-state.test.ts`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check ...`\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs ...`\n- `pnpm tsgo:extensions`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json ...`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json ...`\n- `node scripts/sync-plugin-sdk-exports.mjs --check`\n- `node scripts/check-plugin-sdk-subpath-exports.mjs`\n- `node --max-old-space-size=8192 --import tsx scripts/generate-plugin-sdk-api-baseline.ts --check`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Autoreview rerun clean after accepted findings were fixed.\n",
